✨ Hey beauties! 💖 Ready to unleash your inner glam? As a passionate makeup artist, I’m here to help you shine like the star you are! Whether it’s a casual day look or a full-on glam, I’ve got you covered. Let’s create some magic together! 💄✨ Book your appointment today and let’s make those beauty dreams come true! 💕 #MakeupMagic #BeautyPassion #GlamSquad #MakeupArtist #GlowUp #InstaBeauty

Unleash the artist within and let your passion bloom into a profession.
Step into the enchanting world of beauty with our Basics to Advanced Professional Makeup Course, running from 22nd May to 21st June at our gorgeous studio in M Block Market, GK-2, New Delhi.

Over the course of one transformative month, you’ll master:
	•	The art and science of Color Theory, Color Correction, and Flawless Base Creation
	•	Signature 3D & 4K HD Makeup Techniques
	•	Detailed Eye Artistry – from soft glam to bold smokey eyes, cut crease, jewel tones, Arabic styles & more
	•	Sculpting with Contour, Blush & Highlight
	•	Special modules on Mature Skin Makeup and Male Grooming
	•	Airbrush Makeup – soft, flawless, and camera-perfect

Also included:
	•	Bridal Hairstyling: Classic buns, elegant braids, and precise accessory placement (tika, sheesh patti, passa, etc.)
	•	Dupatta Draping Mastery
	•	Social Media & Reel-Making Class
	•	Photography Training to capture your work like a pro
	•	Self-Makeup Training for personal finesse

You’ll also receive a professionally curated vanity kit and a premium set of MAMA brushes, along with all essential makeup products for practice.

Course Fee: ₹100000/-
Spots are limited, because we believe in intimate learning and deep transformation.
